                "accordion_row_nL9mgY": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "disabled": true,
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Graphic Designer | Gold Coast, Australia",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_NTz9y7": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>Brand Experience Designer</strong></p><p>In-house, Burleigh Waters Gold Coast</p><p><strong> Overview</strong></p><p>Made With Love is entering a new era of brand identity - refined, editorial, and globally recognised. We’re seeking a Graphic Designer with senior design expertise to visually elevate our brand across every touchpoint. This is a pivotal role suited to a highly creative and technically graphic or visual designer who can think strategically, execute beautifully, and align with our brand’s new direction.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>Lead the design of brand decks, look books, and internal presentations to a global standard</p><p>Develop assets for organic and paid campaigns (Meta, Google, Pinterest, TikTok, etc.) with elevated visuals that reflect our brand story</p><p>Create high-quality graphics for web, email, and social using Adobe Suite and Figma</p><p>Collaborate with our Marketing & Ecommerce teams to evolve and refine the visual brand direction</p><p>Translate conceptual briefs into fully designed assets that reflect editorial style and storytelling</p><p>Prepare print-ready artwork for packaging, stationery, boutique materials, and events</p><p>Maintain and evolve the visual brand guidelines and ensure consistency across all global markets and teams</p><p><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>5+ years of graphic design experience with strong Adobe Creative Suite (Photoshop, InDesign, Illustrator) expertise</p><p>Proven ability to create visually elevated work for fashion, luxury, lifestyle or beauty brands</p><p>Figma knowledge a major bonus - for collaboration with web and eCom design</p><p>Deep understanding of digital marketing formats and creative best practices</p><p>High attention to detail, with a passion for aesthetics, typography, and layout</p><p>A collaborative mindset - able to take feedback, lead when needed, and thrive in a creative team</p><p>Experience with global brands or multi-market campaigns is a plus</p><p><strong>You’ll Thrive Here If You...</strong></p><p>Love crafting meaningful visuals that emotionally connect with a customer</p><p>Want to help shape a cult-loved brand as we expand globally</p><p>Think strategically, but aren’t afraid to get hands-on with production</p><p>Are excited by the idea of pushing bridal branding into a new era</p><p><strong>Apply by:</strong><br/><br/><strong>Email</strong> | genea@madewithlovebridal.com</p>",
