                    "text_WLU8Fi": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>We’re looking for warm, fashion-loving Bridal Stylist to join our team in either our Melbourne boutique in a part-time or casual capacity. In this role, you'll help brides find their dream dress, creating unforgettable moments in a beautiful, supportive boutique environment. If you have a natural eye for style, love connecting with people, and can work weekends, we’d love to hear from you. No bridal experience needed, just the right energy and passion!</p><p>Apply either by:<br/><br/><strong>Email</strong> | laura@madewithlovebridal.com</p><p><strong>Linkedin</strong> | <a href=\"https://au.linkedin.com/company/made-with-love-bridal\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://au.linkedin.com/company/made-with-love-bridal\">Here</a></p>",
